<item>
            <title>[HBASE-3146] document feature &quot;hbase.regionserver.codecs&quot;</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-3146</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;a new feature &quot;hbase.regionserver.codecs&quot; allows you to poison pill your regionservers if any of the codecs listed do not test operational on server startup.  &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;the format of the value is &quot;lzo,gz&quot; with strings separated by commas.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12478129">HBASE-3146</key>
            <summary>document feature &quot;hbase.regionserver.codecs&quot;</summary>
